com.squareup.leakcanary

Class ExcludedRefs

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.squareup.leakcanary.ExcludedRefs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class ExcludedRefs
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Prevents specific references from being taken into account when computing the shortest strong reference path from a suspected leaking instance to the GC roots. This class lets you ignore known memory leaks that you known about. If the shortest path matches ExcludedRefs, than the heap analyzer should look for a longer path with nothing matching in ExcludedRefs.
